oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: 308th Engineer Regt. officers
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of the Headquarters and 2nd Batt. officers of the 308th Eng. Regt., 83rd Div. at Neuwied am Rhein, Germany. Maj. Joseph J. Ring is seated in middle row, 5th from left. The sign on the building in the backgroundNeuwieder Papierwaren Tütenfabrik J. H. Krämer (Neuwieder Paper Wares Bag Factory, J. H. Krämer, proprietor). Neuweid am Rhein is approximately 8 miles northwest of Koblenz, Germany. Maj. Joseph Ring was from Franklin, Williamson County, Tennessee.
